title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - PMDG Boeing 737-700 - update 2
description:
In this video we will have a look at the release notes of what has changed in the second update for the PMDG 737-700. This update is focusing mostly in the virtual cockpit and a small number of system behavior issues which were both uncovered by simmers and PMDG. The good thing is they continue to optimize this aircraft and every update it is getting better and better.

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
https://pmdg.com/pmdg-737-700-for-microsoft-flight-simulator/
